This is the code used to create the maps for the paper:

Weibo_Analysis_Redux - Is the Weibo text data analyzed to create the maps and country counts used in the study.

X_BlueSky_Analysis - Is the BlueSky and X/Twitter text data analyzed to create the maps and country counts, as well as the over all 
sentiment charts with the RoBERTa model, and a few other analyses that I did not purpose such as most active posters and topic modeling.

Chinese_RNN - Is this the file I did the sentiment analysis for Chinese testing in, it contains the code used to create the Chinese BERT 
model used to analyze the sentiment. 
